org.opcfoundation.ua.transport

Class Endpoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opcfoundation.ua.transport.Endpoint

  • public class Endpoint
extends java.lang.Object
    Endpoint is a connection point to a server. An endpoint is assigned to a Server using BindingFactory. Endpoint doesn't contain service logic, it is merely description of a connection point.

    This class is hash-equals comparable.

    See Also:
    to bind an endpoint to a {@link Server}
